Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴  我进来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大小姐  请稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没准备好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二学期要开始居然会让你这么忧郁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你怦怦直跳的  最近有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要独自全部承担哦  昴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.35,0:00:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.35,0:00:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是和次郎同学有关的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如被问及「今天内衣的花纹是什么样的」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的  但有什么烦恼的话要跟我说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我踢！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//op//
