Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.79,0:23:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不再是管家了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不再是没种懦弱的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家伙了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.78,0:23:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我会化身为野兽！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成为大胆而又狂野的男人！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了哦  近卫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.31,0:23:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.17,0:23:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.44,0:23:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是记得戴好那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.11,0:23:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.06,0:23:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要戴好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.96,0:23:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.78,0:23:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然章鱼烧还是要浇上蛋黄酱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}（原文かける同时拥有戴和浇的意思）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.90,0:24:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.24,0:24:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集「迷茫管家与懦弱的我」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.24,0:24:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第12话「迷茫管家与懦弱的我」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.52,0:24:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两人究竟能否脱胎换骨呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
